<P>A SERMON, PREACHED BEFORE HIS EXCELLENCY THE PRESIDENT, THE HONORABLE COUNCIL, AND THE HONORABLE THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE STATE OF NEW-HAMPSHIRE, JUNE 7, 1787.</P>
<P>BY JOSEPH BUCKMINSTER, A. M.</P>
<P>PASTOR OF THE FIRST CHURCH IN PORTSMOUTH.</P>
<Q>GIVE ME NOW WISDOM AND KNOWLEDGE, THAT I MAY GO OUT AND COME IN BEFORE THIS PEOPLE.
<BIBL>KING SOLOMON.</BIBL></Q>
<P>PORTSMOUTH: PRINTED, AND TO BE SOLD, BY ROBERT GERRISH.</P>
<P>M.DCC.LXXXVII.</P>
