<P><HI>VOTED, That Mr.</HI> Pickering, <HI>Mr.</HI> Gains, <HI>and Mr.</HI> Emer&s;on, <HI>be a Committee to pre&s;ent the Rev. Mr.</HI> Buckmin&s;ter <HI>with the thanks of this Hou&s;e for his publick performances, and reque&s;t of him a copy of the di&s;cour&s;e delivered before the</HI> General-Court <HI>this day, that the &s;ame way be printed.</HI></P>
